Test Case Title: Content Localization

Test Case ID: LOC-04

Description: Verify that news articles, headlines, and other content are correctly translated and culturally adapted for the selected language edition.

Preconditions:

The application is installed and launched.
The user has selected a language edition.

Test Steps:
Access news articles in different categories.
Verify that headlines, article content, and any related text (e.g., captions, summaries) are translated accurately into the selected language.
Check for cultural adaptation, such as using appropriate terms, references, and context for the region.

Expected Results:

All news content should be correctly translated and culturally adapted to the selected language and region.
